INSERT INTO contracts (producerId, actorId, projectTitle, startDate, endDate, paymentAmount, paymentTerms, status, deliverables, producerSignedAt, actorSignedAt, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 
  (SELECT id FROM users WHERE userRole = 'producer' AND openId = 'demo_prod_1') as producerId,
  (SELECT id FROM users WHERE userRole = 'actor' AND openId = 'demo_actor_1') as actorId,
  'The Last Stand - Feature Film' as projectTitle,
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL -10 DAY) as startDate,
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 35 DAY) as endDate,
  50000 as paymentAmount,
  'Net 30 days after completion' as paymentTerms,
  'active' as status,
  'Lead role performance, 45 days principal photography' as deliverables,
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL -12 DAY) as producerSignedAt,
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL -11 DAY) as actorSignedAt,
  NOW(), NOW()
UNION ALL

  (SELECT id FROM users WHERE userRole = 'producer' AND openId = 'demo_prod_2'),
